{"tid":2515282,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"行李篋藏屍：台檢方今發通緝 促請港府助遣交疑犯","createTime":"2021-05-04T00:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T01:00:31.000Z","uid":25345,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5718cdd2082a7ae0c01dbfc2ed40e67d2c0900eb","tid":2515282,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181203/photo/bkn-20181203171513701-1203_00952_001_01p.jpg?20181203214936\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181203%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181203171513701-1203_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20181203214936&h=52b2b738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港20歲女子潘曉穎今年2月到台灣旅行期間，慘遭殺害棄屍。台灣士林地檢署偵辦8個多月，周一（3日）正式對潘19歲同行男友陳同佳發布通緝，時效長達37年6個月，並同時遞交請求書予法務部，向港府請求協助遣送陳回台接受偵查。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，士林地檢署曾3次向港方請求司法互助，但迄今都未獲回應。台灣法務部表示，由於本案疑犯已返港，在還原釐清犯罪事實方面，尚須香港司法機關協助，台法務部希望香港相關部門能盡快提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n台灣檢方表示，陳同佳雖仍遭羈押，但未來又不會以殺人案定罪；死者父親曾多次表達，希望台檢方能向香港政府請求遣送陳回台接受追訴及審判，惟港台之間並無引渡協議。"},{"pid":"11964eed1257e9e45891283e786ea5741351eca8","tid":2515282,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:55:29.000Z","msg":"佳佳仲係安全屋好食好住<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99801576755c1aadeb804914fe6686591562eff","tid":2515282,"uid":70527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:58:08.000Z","msg":"逃犯天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e5399e925d3961a4d7c35b41618445dcff7315","tid":2515282,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:59:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea3514f50405585c681a8901f32630548346369","tid":2515282,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T01:00:31.000Z","msg":"佳佳喺豪宅happy 緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}